content.location: Between Overly Hung Boulder and Sledgehammer formation.

content.description: Little boulder that sits by the Sledgehammer. One problem on it that was done by the legendary Bob Murray. It is a little awkward if you aren't familiar with the beta. It can be strenuous on your arms and shoulders. Classic problem when you figure it out.
